{{Infobox vacuum tube |image = [[Image:866 mercury rectifier 1.jpeg|250px|thumb| 866A Mercury rectifier]] |caption = Westinghouse 866A mercury vapor half-wave rectifier tube. |classification = [[Diode]] <!-- Mandatory -->
